messages.message:
hi all, a request that @Kerry and I’m sure many have had. “When are we releasing and who are we releasing to”:
I’ve added a link called “Release Schedule” to our Instabase Engineering sites link: https://sites.google.com/s/1n7hWhLDizWv4LwYtV4BcNOddiqgzMw8m/p/1rC8EIBtfYtnU2PylMP4ScVOwm7vbQQAL/edit

This spreadsheet should help you answer the main questions you have related to releases. Thanks @Ashish for organizing this. Also make sure to keep this document up-to-date when you have a request for Ashish and want to add a customer to the “Deployment Targets” column
